T1  - Robustly Strategic Consumption–Portfolio Rules with Informational Frictions
AU  - Luo, Yulei
Y1  - 2016/10/13
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2017/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2016.2553
